n><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">z</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">then</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">else</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"gr\">sorry</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Comparing to the first example I can't use pattern matching on <code>x</code> anymore and don't get any information in the <code>else</code> block.</p>",
